{"tid":187401,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[音樂概念] 有冇人成日想夾一d歌但又搵唔到人夾？","createTime":"2017-04-05T02:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T15:33:27.000Z","uid":93484,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d27e1565897f6abe3426965ef1817191bd9d7ddb","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"身為樂手/vocal/dj/rapper/beatboxer 的你<br />\n係咪心目中成日都會有d歌好想玩<br />\n但因為搵唔夠腳夾而一直無機會玩？<br />\n<br />\n以下落來小弟想試下攪一個名 [音樂有緣人]的計劃<br />\n好簡單首先你地先提議出一首歌<br />\n之後列名自己係呢首歌的position 例: vocal/guitar/....等等<br />\n然後再列出你想尋找的有緣人 例: bass/dj/rapper ....等等<br />\n咁我會將你地的歌單定期係呢個post同埋我將會開的tg到更新<br />\n最後成團後就可以進行下一步的計劃<br />\n<br />\n點解我會講下一步？<br />\n因為除左去band房夾歌之外<br />\n其實我仲想將大家心目中的愛歌記錄下來<br />\n呢樣野容後再講<br />\n<br />\n我先來發辦<br />\n先來首香港我最愛的歌手Eason的 &quot;太陽照常升起&quot;<br />\n<br />\n小弟係vocal<br />\n想搵Keyboard/guitar/bass/鼓佬 一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfffe1c1ae1ba5e0d0a19e362e48040ae9f46d06","tid":187401,"uid":4301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"小弟結他<br />\n想搵人搵post-hardcore類型 vocal<br />\n咩歌都可以"},{"pid":"31513c7dbbe98df35b359cb9e7e5ce069f53afc1","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟結他<br />\n想搵人搵post-hardcore類型 vocal<br />\n咩歌都可以</blockquote><br />\nChing你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以簡單介紹一下Post-hardcore<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有冇邊d樂隊可以推介一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fbe61cd962124e9af35a841f7b9f4904dc33dd","tid":187401,"uid":4301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟結他<br />\n想搵人搵post-hardcore類型 vocal<br />\n咩歌都可以</blockquote><br />\nChing你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b