s/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然同我原想有少少出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都試下整理下大家的要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟 - 搵guitar/keyboard//bass percussion人 玩Eason的 太陽照常升起<br />\n<br />\n笨撚吹屎眼 - 搵post-hardcore類型 vocal<br />\n<br />\n希望你讓我下沉~ - 揾pop嘅結他同cajon<br />\n<br />\n走光之美少女 - 仲未知搵咩的鼓手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外賣仔阿銀 - 玩咩都得的結他手<br />\n<br />\n麒麟之才 - 玩中英文rock的結他手 <br />\n<br />\nEjimaHarushi - 電 guitar + vocal 想搵人作野 <br />\n<br />\n宮崎葵 - vocal 搵鼓佬夾 indie rock<br />\n<br />\n貓 - 本身係keyboard想唱歌 <br />\n<br />\n連登好多低質會然 - bass手想玩swing的歌 <br />\n<br />\n大家可以留底 tg 咁我可以開個group等大家搵下人同吹下水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個tg : delusionblue"},{"pid":"d3d19b47f971957252e5d404c3cf8fa3a32a72b5","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電 guitar + vocal，<br />\n識作下曲(主要係日本仔個d jazz chord 底既野，聽開東京事變、椎名林檎、polkadot stingray個類)<br />\n填詞好廢，<br />\n最近開始玩cubase，<br />\n錄下野玩編曲，<br />\n成日作到一半冇靈感作落去，<br />\n想搵下有冇人有心機同我一齊作野。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n師兄作野都係作cubase野 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358407dfc6e0ef876b1625509312950a255108f3","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾結他手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩咩類型都冇所謂</blockquote><br />\n有冇邊隻歌最鍾意的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我聽歌好雜食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果講最中意就supper moment 同ganleryus</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nＧanleryus屬於咩類型 ?"},{"pid":"134a254faeba29d523ead6df4e61dca3b4f8e7d3","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係夾散band? <br />\n好似幾得意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n其實我原意係為左1首歌而夾<br />\n好似我心裡面有好多冷門歌想玩<br />\n但你好難要你自己隊band去練咁多歌<br />\n所以我想試下搵到一d所有人都鍾意果首歌的人<br />\n咁首歌夾左出來d的feel都會好好多<br />\n同大家都會落力好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6cdeb09c44e6598babd8aeb8afd66174f24d47","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟結他<br />\n想搵人搵post-hardcore類型 vocal<br />\n咩歌都可以</blockquote><br />\nChing你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以簡單介紹一下Post-hardcore<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有冇邊d樂隊可以推介一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以試下聽coldrain</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncoldrain 好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3fb9625d6ef0816841ec2b039ff7748b50c4ec","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想夾，但沒朋友夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你留底你的postion 你想搵的樂手/vocal<br />\n同你tg 咁我定期列出來等有興趣的人可以搵你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a16704615bb88dc2974ccb3f95c2d1ddd0bf099","tid":187401,"uid":93484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾結他手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b